text: Abryna coenosa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Newman in 1842. It is known from Taiwan and the Philippines.BioLib.cz - Abryna coenosa. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==Subspecies== * Abryna coenosa coenosa Newman, 1842 * Abryna coenosa mindanaonis Breuning, 1980 * Abryna coenosa superba Pic, 1932 ==References== Category:Pteropliini Category:Beetles described in 1842
